Company Profile:Newton Circus is a technology and community development firm that is an industry leader in Singapore's rapidly growing hackathon industry. In addition to this, Newton Circus is one of the fastest expanding social enterprises in Singapore, subscribing firmly to the philosophy that doing good is good business.Find out more about Newton Circus and its various projects and ventures at www.newton-circus.com
Job Description:The successful applicant for the graphic design intern role will report directly to Newton Circus' in-house designer, assisting with major projects as well as handling some smaller scale assignments.The successful applicant will have the opportunity to not only learn from experienced members of their chosen field, but also be in an excellent position to network with leaders of many varied industries due to the nature of the work Newton Circus is engaged in.PREREQUISITES:- Must be proficient in Adobe Creative Suite (Illustrator, Photoshop, Indesign, etc)- Good layout skills- Good grasp on typography- Must have sound understanding of web and mobile design and latest web trends
